  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d6d5e53d86886ea00937bd65f5ad4e513e0d0858.png\" alt=\"Banner\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a0cc41ac8ed63c6b0d3684a5b87ea1134363272c_0.webp\" alt=\"Social+\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://docs.mongenscave.com/free-products/playervisibility\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d09eb5d615be9e47efa94b7909ef02b9096e5c80_0.webp\" alt=\"Docs\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MRr8af1.gif\" alt=\"Visibility Item\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MnNkaf6.gif\" alt=\"Hide New Players\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/69e9c13ee276f4a76e8be72e7107b1a4a662b291.png\" alt=\"DB\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4f4045c064f3f903bc50005ee9e77a3a961e6353.png\" alt=\"FOLIA\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/27ee71e77e7d68c032d82f08ae63d21b78b89a5a.png\" alt=\"Feature 1\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://dc.mongenscave.com/\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4e8d4e042a9b0899f93642800228c395027a3f98.png\" alt=\"Feature 2\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>Text Transcript</summary>\nPlayerVisibility\nMake waiting players comfortable with a simple plugin now!\n\nFREE Discord Support | Full documented plugin\n\nFeatures:\n- Visibility Item\n- Hide New Players\n- Database Support: MySQL, H2 & SQLite\n- Version Support: 1.21.x - 1.18\n- Optimized Plugin\n- Folia Support\n\nMajor Features:\n- Customizable Items:\nThe visibility items are fully customizable, and the plugin supports HEX color codes and textured items as well! (CustomModelData)\n\n- Multiple Server Support:\nSave Visibility settings to a MySQL database for flexible use across multiple Lobby servers simultaneously.\n</details>\n\n",
